{"tid":1469953,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"陳雲：機場的事，絕對不要道歉！同大家講下謠言戰術，rumour tactics。","createTime":"2019-08-14T03:41:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T04:41:39.000Z","uid":295300,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2a6a98c767091894596caae6bc59d665e1cae271","tid":1469953,"uid":295300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:41:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NA8fcop.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNA8fcop.png&h=7d042a8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n陳雲：機場的事，絕對不要道歉！同大家講下謠言戰術，rumour tactics。因為謠言需要用民間文學和民間藝術形態，故此是民俗學的學術研究題目，我在德國讀書的時候，研究過二次大戰的謠言戰術，納粹集團及英美盟軍也用。<br />\n<br />\n示威者在機場犯錯，滋擾旅客，拘禁北京記者，阻礙警方救援，是否要道歉呢，甚至要做圖道歉呢？<br />\n<br />\n你以為你的對手是無權力而任你說有食藥、無食藥而恆久寬恕你的學者陳雲嗎？你的對手是謠言高手中國共產黨，殘酷狡猾的獨裁蘇維埃政府。中共在製造滿清政府的林維喜事件、七七盧溝橋日本士兵失踪的事件，之後出動武警或民兵。你的一個錯誤的舉動，足以引發共產黨派武警團進入機場維持國際航班的秩序&mdash;&mdash;在香港警方的邀請及授權之下，香港警方可以將中共的武警納入香港臨時編制的。香港有英國殖民地留下的警方編制，可以將英聯邦的警察納入臨時特務編制而不違反條例的。中共的武警團進入機場，將文明禮貌處事，國際旅客也會諒解。一旦武警團進入香港警察編制，香港就馬上進入烏克蘭戰鬥模式，但我們不是烏克蘭人！這個要知己知彼。我們很多人準備放棄香港移民的，也有外國護照在手。<br />\n<br />\n中共造謠沒問題，他們自己人也不信的，只是服從淫威。香港示威者的道歉，就是自己承認錯誤，不打自招，給了中共堅實的材料來做宣傳，那麼不單止大陸人會信、香港人也會信、國際社會也會信。你水洗都不清，因為你往自己身上潑污水！<br />\n<br />\n好彩機管局裡面有聰明人，昨晚懂得申請法庭禁制令，救了示威者。請停止機場的無聊滋擾行為，改為在市區球場公園做和平集會和展覽，請外國領事做監護，遇到中共特務滋擾就散去，由得他們在外國人的親見之下破壞展品。領事走了你就散去，不要佔領，不要過夜。出事的。"},{"pid":"1a7187c43a0d16baee4bc0f1f6bf5c0c8416a37a","tid":1469953,"uid":295300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:42:39.000Z","msg":"自推十次救大家<br />\n好彩有禁制令<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c9ec38d59a685d1fd5e9c6ce21a5818bd7db542","tid":1469953,"uid":295300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:43:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0be168fc8ba8a4abcf5b82172575babe43eb6d5a","tid":1469953,"uid":295300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:43:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0deb6e6653c0f276917a8e1799c090b070aeae04","tid":1469953,"uid":295300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:44:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36979d07aec08ffe52a433537af4c9dc066481b8","tid":1469953,"uid":295300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:44:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb4839a93727dfe0306440ef485fc3db0d4d6b61","tid":1469953,"uid":295300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:44:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d7f6e89ed4830e552a63e9eeb26b4b965a5e848","tid":1469953,"uid":295300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:44:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66c0ce0d86aa9843704347e477b582e01c17e5a8","tid":1469953,"uid":295300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:44:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"769661be3932fb291a73b75b5c57134fa0ca8c95","tid":1469953,"uid":295300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:45:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6094a0d380db8055675f2cfc95493a619556335","tid":1469953,"uid":295300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:45:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c976d36a18f94b3623a24ba2dc1d1b8c6132ab8","tid":1469953,"uid":2748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:56:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"093464ed786ae171b878c78aa3efd30da90f087f","tid":1469953,"uid":149630,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:08:59.000Z","msg":"陳雲：<br />\n做錯事不道歉，是違反道德的啊。這個當然，但我們不是在小學課室，由班長和班主任裁判，我們是在戰場上，警察、法官、電視台、報紙、觀眾都是中共的人。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你道歉，對方就有材料展開政治謠言宣傳，而且要求你再為其他你無做過的事道歉（例如毆打北京記者），之後你拒絕，他們就向你開火射擊。</span></span>做錯了事就馬上走，不是道歉！<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">普選勝利了，在民選元首認為安全的情況</span></span>，才為以往的錯失道歉，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">道歉也是元首來做，不是民眾來做</span></span>，賠償也是用政府的錢，不是民間眾籌。"},{"pid":"6f5d2c8849277ab05d0cab68281e3095cf4a6033","tid":1469953,"uid":293980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:11:09.000Z","msg":"推。。"},{"pid":"4d8b8381e212a87ed6df5bb7a9ed0a204818774b","tid":1469953,"uid":39433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:41:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}